 P2y.jp  https://p2y.jp 2023 年 8 月 21 日星期一 18:43:45 +0000 zh每小时1 https://wordpress.org/?v=6.2.2 https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/cropped-logo_2023_150x150-32x32.png P2y.jp https://p2y.jp 32 32 166157578
任天堂宣布马里奥配音演员查尔斯·马丁内特退休并任命为亲善大使https://p2y.jp/nintendo-announces-retirement-of-mario-voice-actor-charles-martinet-and-appointment-as-goodwill-ambassador/ https://p2y.jp/nintendo-announces-retirement-of-mario-voice-actor-charles-martinet-and-appointment-as-goodwill-ambassador/#respondp2y_admin Mon, 21 Aug 2023 18:42:45 +0000 ゲーム任天堂Charles Martinet(チャールズ・マーティネー)Nintendo SwitchNINTENDO64TwitterYouTubeスーパーマリオマリオ声優 https://p2y.jp/?p=99268 <p> 2023年8月21日，任天堂宣布，曾负责马里奥配音的查尔斯·马丁内特（Charles Martinet）退休，并被任命为该角色的亲善大使。]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/nintendo-announces-retirement-of-mario-voice-actor-charles-martinet-and-appointment-as-goodwill-ambassador/">任天堂宣布扮演任天堂马里奥的配音演员查尔斯·马丁内特 (Charles Martinet) 退休并任命他为亲善大使的消息首先</a>出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p>任天堂于 2023 年 8 月 21 日宣布，马里奥的配音演员查尔斯·马丁内特 (Charles <strong>Martinet)</strong>已退出该角色，并被任命为该角色的亲善大使。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-attachment-id="99285" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/nintendo-announces-retirement-of-mario-voice-actor-charles-martinet-and-appointment-as-goodwill-ambassador/nintendo_announces_retirement_of_mario_voice_actor_charles_martinet_and_appointment_as_goodwill_ambassador/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nintendo_announces_retirement_of_mario_voice_actor_charles_martinet_and_appointment_as_goodwill_ambassador.png" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="nintendo_announces_retirement_of_mario_voice_actor_charles_martinet_and_appointment_as_goodwill_ambassador" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nintendo_announces_retirement_of_mario_voice_actor_charles_martinet_and_appointment_as_goodwill_ambassador.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nintendo_announces_retirement_of_mario_voice_actor_charles_martinet_and_appointment_as_goodwill_ambassador.png" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="675" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nintendo_announces_retirement_of_mario_voice_actor_charles_martinet_and_appointment_as_goodwill_ambassador.png" alt="" class="wp-image-99285"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：X（推特）<br> ©任天堂</figcaption></figure><p>查尔斯·马丁内特（Charles Martinet）自1996年（平成8年）发行的任天堂64软件《超级马里奥64》中首次为马里奥配音以来，一直担任配音演员。</p><p>另外，事实证明，马丁先生将不会参加最新的马里奥系列《超级马里奥兄弟奇迹》。因此，在这部作品之后，似乎将有新的声优来为马里奥配音。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="超级马里奥兄弟奇迹 [任天堂直播 2023.6.21]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nnCt1HUIqHo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><div class="wkyij64e4363fe8a59" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
